item.title: Matrix 718 rsps Help me please!
item.dc:creator: @Lucas7 Lucas7
item.description:
@Lucas7 wrote:

What you are missing are xTeas. By the looks of the menu bar, it appears you are trying to load maybe a 716 or 718 cache and you do not have the mapdata for it.

I wouldn’t kill yourself looking for the xTeas since to my knowledge only two servers have them Matrix and XLite.

Also, usually people who are able to get these xTeas usually don’t want to share them since they are so hard to get.
